AB  - We propose a hierarchical entanglement routing protocol over the nodes of a quantum network. The objectives are to develop realistic timing parameters of entanglement operations, design the protocol procedure steps, and conduct simulations and performance evaluation. The work has applications to link layer protocols for quantum networks and the future quantum internet.
