TI  - Binding Affinity and Mechanism of Six PFAS with Human Serum Albumin: Insights from Multi-Spectroscopy, DFT and Molecular Dynamics Approaches
LA  - eng
JF  - Toxics
VL  - 12
IS  - 1
PY  - 2024
