TI  - Charge order near the antiferromagnetic quantum critical point in the trilayer high T<sub>c</sub> cuprate HgBa<sub>2</sub>Ca<sub>2</sub>Cu<sub>3</sub>O<sub>8+δ</sub> [arXiv]
LA  - eng
