TI  - Hybrid Trusted Quantum Key Distribution Network Routing Scheme for Power Grid Environment
LA  - eng
JF  - 2024 10th International Conference on Computer and Communications (iccc)
SP  - 422
EP  - 427
PY  - 2024
SN  - 28377109
