TI  - Molecular design and synthesis of highly soluble hole transporting materials based on phenylnaphthalene cores for solution-processible OLEDs
LA  - eng
JF  - Dyes and Pigments
VL  - 222
PY  - 2024
SN  - 18733743, 01437208
