TI  - A natural dye-based Schottky diode with observed quantum tunnelling and determined trap density, mobility, and excellent sensitivity and nonlinearity
LA  - eng
JF  - Bulletin of Materials Science
VL  - 47
IS  - 2
PY  - 2024
SN  - 09737669, 02504707
